{"tid":456801,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"食熱氣野開聲","createTime":"2017-11-03T08:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T09:45:04.000Z","uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9f0a440d6a143439de7965ecb774a4ba499369","tid":456801,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"有無人好似我咁唔知點解食熱氣野反而會即刻開到聲...?好似m記，煎炸野嗰啲。反而平時點鳩叫都開唔到但一食熱氣野就好快開到聲"},{"pid":"a2475b5dcf349fad49c643925a2c2018095ac2a7","tid":456801,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似唔會"},{"pid":"f6e13bf9447f01ef4b98cd433d5e874be04f24f7","tid":456801,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似唔會</blockquote><br />\n我就係唔知點解會有咁既情況，想揾下原因，但又揾唔到，所以想睇下有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3428a3d8d418871ac724ed8ad312f8663a6915c5","tid":456801,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"係咪本身你用錯力發聲？<br />\n我黎講食野係會的<br />\n但無話特別熱氣野衰啲"},{"pid":"ee15ea17a25690e075ccc9050eb9d61321a9f0b3","tid":456801,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪本身你用錯力發聲？<br />\n我黎講食野係會的<br />\n但無話特別熱氣野衰啲</blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n但食完熱氣野返而條聲帶順左好多，正正係開左聲既狀態，我想揾解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b2aa73503bcb2b612c8a6ce1ec7d8ac3a9807c","tid":456801,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:44:01.000Z","msg":"熱漲冷縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8fb3ac10eaa061ef8e1e88eb3ac1d8ccdf962d","tid":456801,"uid":74821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱漲冷縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好既解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但普通熱野無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}